# Copy to .env (git-ignored) for the Claude narrative read. The linter, the
# tests, and the score run offline with no key, so this is only for the read.

# With a key set, claude-opus-4-8 reads the narrative arc the rules cannot score
# and prints below the score, by default. It is advisory and never changes the
# score. Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com/ and `pip install anthropic`.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
